Package client.view

Class Controller

java.lang.Object
client.view.Controller
Direct Known Subclasses:
ActivationController, ChatController, ConstructionController, GameController, GameWonController, LobbyController, LoginController, MenuController, OnePlayerController, OthersController, PickDamageController, PlayCardController, PlayerMatController, ProgrammingController
public abstract class Controller
extends java.lang.Object
Abstract super class of all view-controller, which also stores information and required attributes for dragging and dropping between ProgrammingController and PlayerMatController.
Author:
simon, sarah
